name: 'A Brand New Day' Autographed CD+Photo Bundle
description:
Package includes our new CD signed by the group, plus a signed photo, and a Daves Highway guitar logo sticker for your notebook, bumper or wherever.

Enjoy the group’s latest work, 'A Brand New Day' is their second full-length album that features 14 songs and a variety of original and classic tunes performed by the genre-bending siblings. 
 
Produced by Andrew Reed of Artists International Media and recorded at Sedgwick Studios tucked away in the mountains of Asheville, NC, A Brand New Day continues to explore the teen siblings’ musical interests. 

Track List:
1. Unclouded Day-Prelude
2. Words
3. Look With Mercy
4. A Brand New Day
5. Here Comes The Sun
6. Choose To Fly
7. A Song For The Rest Of My Life
8. Brighter Than A Star
9. Washed By The Water
10. Everything We Need
11. You Are The Rock
12. You Don't Have To Move That Mountain
13. Unclouded Day
14. Edelweiss (Bonus Track)

name: All Music Pack - All 3 of Daves Highway's CDs
description:
Enjoy all 3 of the group's studio recordings plus stickers and photos, too!  We'll even autograph our newest photo as a souvenir keepsake. 

'JUST FOR YOU' includes the YouTube favorites JESUS MESSIAH, BOONDOCKS, AMAZING GRACE, and a medley of three Christmas songs to finish 2009 on the right note. 

The six song EP was produced in Nashville by Grammy and Dove award-winning producer Charlie Peacock (Switchfoot, NewSong).

Track List:
-Boondocks
-Jesus Messiah
-O Come, O Come, Emmanuel
-O Little Town Of Bethlehem
-Go Tell It On The Mountain
-Amazing Grace (My Chains Are Gone)

'All This Time' was released in September 2011 featuring 11 brand new songs by Daves Highway.  Produced by Sam Ashworth (Michael W. Smith, Sixpence None the Richer) at The Art House in Nashville,  the group offers authentic country folk blends in 3 part harmony.   

CD Track list:
-All This Time
-Call You Home
-Lay It Down
-Summertime
-It Is Well With My Soul
-Way Of Love
-Right Where You Oughta Be
-Love Is Everything
-Just Another Day
-Perfect Peace
-The Brightness Of Jesus
